{"lemma":"ضارَّةٍ","slug":"ضارَّةٍ","root":"ض.ر.ر","root_slug":"ض-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-ر-ر","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ضارّ","root":"ضرر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25659","n26142","n26186"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of ضَرَّ (ḍarra): that causes harm, harmful, injurious, noxious","tags":["active","form-of","participle"],"examples":[{"text":"وَمَا هُم بِضَارِّينَ بِهِ مِنْ أَحَدٍ إِلَّا بِإِذْنِ ٱللّٰهِ"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to harm"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to harm"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25659","headword_ar":"ضارّهُ","root":"Dr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDaAr~apN","text_ar":"مُضَارَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaraArN","text_ar":"ضَرَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He harmed him, injured him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurt him, in return,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in requital:"},{"kind":"text","text":"whence the saying in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lA Darara","text_ar":"لا ضَرَرَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA DiraAra fiY AlA_isolaAmi","text_ar":"وَلَا ضِرَارَ فِى الاـِسْلَامِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There shall be no harming, injuring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of one man by another,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the first instance, nor in return,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"requital, in El-Islám:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA: *)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DiraArN","text_ar":"ضِرَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDaAr~apN","text_ar":"مُضَارَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or, accord. to some, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DararN","text_ar":"ضَرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and in the phrase in a trad. mentioned above, is added as a corroborative. (TA.) See also 1."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDaAr~apN","text_ar":"مُضَارَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the case of a testament is the not executing it; or the violating it in part; or the bequeathing to any unfit person or persons; and the like; contrary to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sun~ap","text_ar":"سُنَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He disagreed with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"differed from, him; dissented from him; was contrary, opposed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repugnant, to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acted contrarily, contrariously, adversely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in opposition, to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAlafahu","text_ar":"خالَفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) And hence, accord. to some, the saying in a trad., (O, K,) relating to the seeing God on the day of resurrection, (O,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tuDaAr~uwna fiY ruw^oyatihi","text_ar":"لَا تُضَارُّونَ فِى رُوْيَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ye will not differ, one from another, nor dispute together, respecting"},{"kind":"text","text":"the truth of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the seeing Him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, O, * TA;) because of his manifest appearance: (Zj, TA:) or the meaning is,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tuDaAm~uwna","text_ar":"لَا تُضَامُّونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and thus some relate it, (TA,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ye will not draw yourselves together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straiten one another;"},{"kind":"text","text":"one saying to another “ Show me Him, ” like as people do in looking at the new moon, but each will by himself have the sight of Him: (TA:) or, as some say, it is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taDaAr~uwna","text_ar":"لَا تَضَارُّونَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tataDaAr~uwna","text_ar":"تَتَضَارُّونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taDaAm~uwna","text_ar":"لَا تَضَامُّونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which is the same in signification as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tuDaAm~uwna","text_ar":"لَا تُضَامُّونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], i. e. with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA, and so in one of my"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1776},{"kind":"text","text":"copies of the S:) and some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lA tuDaAruwna","text_ar":"لا تُضَارُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~ayoru","text_ar":"الضَّيْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mgh, TA;) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ye will not be hurt;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ye will not hurt one another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dyr","text_ar":"ضير"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tuDaAmuwn","text_ar":"لَا تُضَامُون"},{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~ayomu","text_ar":"الضَّيْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh, TA.) ―         -b3-  See also 4; and the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazaw~aja EalaY","text_ar":"تَزَوَّجَ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDaAr~apK","text_ar":"مُضَارَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dir~N","text_ar":"ضِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","Zj","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n26142","headword_ar":"ضَارَهُ","root":"Dwr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaDuwru","text_ar":"يَضُورُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaArahu","text_ar":"ضَارَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaDiyru","text_ar":"يَضِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dyr","text_ar":"ضير"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n26186","headword_ar":"ضَارَهُ","root":"Dyr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaDiyru","text_ar":"يَضِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DayorN","text_ar":"ضَيْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, A, Msb, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaArahu","text_ar":"ضَارَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaDuwru","text_ar":"يَضُورُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaworN","text_ar":"ضَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"harmed, injured, hurt, mischiefed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"damaged, him; i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~ahu","text_ar":"ضَرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aDar~a bihi","text_ar":"اَضَرَّ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA mim~aA laA","text_ar":"هٰذَا مِمَّا لَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaDiyruka","text_ar":"يَضِيرُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is of the things that will not harm thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lawo faEalotahu lamo yaDiroka","text_ar":"لَوْ فَعَلْتَهُ لَمْ يَضِرْكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hadst thou done it, it had not harmed thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA Dayora Ealayoka","text_ar":"لَا ضَيْرَ عَلَيْكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"No harm shall befall thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yaDiyruka","text_ar":"مَا يَضِيرُكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY AlD~ab~i SiyodN","text_ar":"عَلَى الضَّبِّ صِيْدٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yaDur~uka","text_ar":"مَا يَضُرُّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"q. v. (A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dr","text_ar":"ضر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And Ks says that he had heard (from one of the people of El-' Áliyeh. TA) the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yanofaEuniY *`lika walaA yaDuwruniY","text_ar":"لَا يَنْفَعُنِى ذٰلِكَ وَلَا يَضُورُنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That will not benefit me, nor will it harm me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) See also a reading of a phrase in a trad. cited in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dr","text_ar":"ضر"},{"kind":"text","text":". conj. 3."}],"source_refs":["S","M","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}